        "description": "Register a new user account.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- username (string, required): 3-20 characters\n- email (string, required): Valid email format\n- password (string, required): Minimum 8 characters\n- role (enum, required): COMPANY, WORKER, or ADMIN\n\n**Response:**\n- accessToken (string): JWT access token for API authentication\n- refreshToken (string): Refresh token for obtaining new access tokens\n- tokenType (string): Token type (always \"Bearer\")\n- expiresIn (long): Access token expiration time in seconds (900 = 15 minutes)\n\n**Token Lifetimes:**\n- Access token: 15 minutes\n- Refresh token: 30 days\n\n**Note:** COMPANY role automatically creates a Company entity for the user."
